        <mxCell id="banner_text" value="&lt;div style='padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 15px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;'&gt;&lt;b style='color:#3B50D2;'&gt;Human-in-the-Loop (HITL):&lt;/b&gt; The Pentester retains absolute oversight &amp;mdash; every critical agent action requires explicit approval before execution. The AI Assistant operates within workflow rules and cannot bypass approval gates.&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
